title: Malia Obama Went to a Dorm Party, Played Beer Pong and Did Shots - Photo - newsR
text: Imagine being 17 and going on a tour of college campuses to see which would suit you better when the time comes to apply. First Daughter Malia Obama did just that last weekend and even attended a dorm party - and the Internet completely lost it. A photo of Malia standing by a beer pong table has emerged online, after it was posted on Snapchat, from where it leaked.
